title: Vazquez and Hemmerich Advance in Doubles for @OspreyWTEN in Day 1 of ITA Regionals
text: won their first round contest, sweeping their opponents from Georgia Southern, 8-0. In singles play, all three players fell in their opening round matches and will look to continue play in the consolation rounds. fell in her match to No. 58 Silvia Garcia of Georgia, 6-2, 7-6 (8). Hemmerich dropped her match to No. 32 Belinda Woolcock of Florida, 6-3, 6-0. Vazquez fell to No. 38 Kourtney Keegan of Florida, 6-1, 6-1. Play continues tomorrow with the Round of 32 in doubles play and the singles consolation rounds.
